definitions.definition: A horn -like elongated rostrum on the head of soldier termites of the subfamily Nasutiterminae , capable of producing and spraying noxious secretions for defense .
A prolongation on the front of the head of a cranefly .

main_definition: ( entomology ) A horn -like elongated rostrum on the head of soldier termites of the subfamily Nasutiterminae , capable of producing and spraying noxious secretions for defense .
